Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just did what you had to do\Nas a doctor... It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the sandwiches\Nand get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to survive,\Nand save as many people as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:49.20,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Nina... What do you intend to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:54.60,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Do you intend to try to\NKill him again...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.04,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,I brought him back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:03.35,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,I brought that monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.41,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This arteriovenous malformation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,contains many blood vessels...\NCut away all of the inflowing arteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat all of the outflowing veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal of the nidus is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... that certainly went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He did the clipping\Nvery quickly, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a magnificent operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his first surgery after\Nan extended leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but the talent of this genius\Nkeeps growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!\N—Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:37.57,Title,Episode Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,350)\fad(1021,918)}Pursued
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.51,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was wonderful, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.11,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,That wasn't news about me,\Nbut about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.68,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.13,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,But that's because you did\Nsuch a perfect job last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:28.79,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,as part of Father's team.\NI'm sure Father is grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.62,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,After all, you're the one who has\Nraised the fame of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.99,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who is grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.83,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to your father that\NI am able to work here in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.04,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.63,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,If you stick with Father,\Nyour future is guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.55,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It won't be long before Father\Nbecomes Chairman of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.89,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Then you'll quickly become\NChief of Surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.48,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,and in time, Hospital Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.99,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,And then, I will be the Director's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:01.59,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,You must make me happy, now.\NHardships do not become me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.19,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,You want to go out on a date...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.06,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm afraid you cannot...\NThe mistress is resting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take much of her time.\NI will leave very shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, please return again\Nafter making an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that noise...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm terribly sorry, Ma'am.\NIt's the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Police...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again,\NMiss Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for the help you gave me\Non your father's case, nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lunge of the Federal Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave us, Horst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just a useless detective\Nwho couldn't even close that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been able to\Nmaintain this residence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,even after your father's death.\NI am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I do believe all of the furnishing\Nis even grander than it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to see how wealthy\NI've become with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,my inheritance from my father\Nand settlements from my divorces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I lack nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see anything you want\Nplease help yourself to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, as long as I have my liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to have a look at\Nsomething... This necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you don't remember...\NIt's something from nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple print,\Nbut if you look at it carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a wonderful piece\Nwith a complex weave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This really gave me a hard time.\NAfter all, it's been nine years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But luckily, this comes from a shop\Nthat had a limited number of these
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,made for their best customers.\NAnd on their list...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I found your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you purchase this\Nand give it to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This plays a key role\Nin another murder, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given countless gifts to men,\Nso I can't remember them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The men who approach me\Nare all after my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't remember!\NThey're all after my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a single person\Nwho truly loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I took each one\Nto the cleaners with each divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of them. Good for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something too?\NYou want something? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember it'll cost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remember anything,\Nplease give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you come,\Nbe sure to bring a bottle of liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.62,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.13,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eva, won't you talk to\Nyour father for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.19,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.04,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I just operated\Non an emergency case
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.60,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,in the order in which\Nhe was brought in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.54,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,That's... your engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.21,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:32.76,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:40.93,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.36,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Why, Dr. Norden,\Ndon't you look elegant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.73,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,As do you! You're more beautiful\Nthan ever tonight, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Horst, have my car readied!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Hess, you seem to be\Nmuch better. Your color is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll be able to go home\Nsometime this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter is getting\Nmarried next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to attend her wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that should be fine.\NJust don't overdo it at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had resigned myself to not going,\Nbut thanks to you, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was due to your own efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With you at my side,\NI feel as though I can be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,not only at my daughter's,\Nbut at my grandchildren's weddings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly an excellent doctor.\NPlease stay here at this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Dr. Tenma... You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I must make my rounds now.\NI'm too busy. Please turn them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gone through so much,\Nhaven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.92,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Father... Are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.40,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.58,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.78,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eva...\N—Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.38,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard, but you must\Npull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:11.46,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.79,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Give me back my father!\NFather...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.37,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.77,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Please, I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.91,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.80,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenzo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost some weight, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you were on extended leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you should rest yourself\Nfrom time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a glutton for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost some weight too,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So much has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard the rumors,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring... Do you remember?\NTen years ago, in spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We often went driving together...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to swim in the river\Nin that season...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurriedly stopped you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, I haven't got time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After three failed marriages,\NI finally realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one who truly loved me\Nwas you, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your feelings,\Nbut I just can't accept them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye.\N—Wait, Kenzo! I didn't say a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When the police came\Nto ask about your necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something bad\Nconnected with that necktie of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's the tie that I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do as I say,\NI'll keep quiet about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the police about that necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who killed my father\Nnine years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Bring Dr. Tenma in\Nas a person of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But there isn't enough evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Fortner couple\Nand Maurer murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about\Nthe killing at Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!\N—Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This might allow us\Nto solve a lot of murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Resignation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this,\NDr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I'm acting selfishly, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There seem to be various\Nstrange rumors about you, recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't believe any of them.\NPlease think this over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... T-Tenma...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm me... What?! The police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is a murder suspect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Close off the exits from each wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the back exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on there?\NHurry up and search the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!\NYou're interfering with the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma would never kill anyone!\N—That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're indebted to him\Nfor saving our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!\N—Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seems to be going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole bunch\Nof patrol cars, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see... I wonder what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just drop me off\Nin front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. You're busy as always,\Naren't you, Dr. Tenma...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:28.26,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I... I have a surgery waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.27,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Wait! Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.96,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.23,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Don't worry. Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.77,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I'll save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.47,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I am not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.15,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}You say there's\Na flaw in my character?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.44,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.09,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}You call yourself a doctor,\Nbut you're just money hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.69,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}That bastard... That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.19,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}He's better off dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:00.50,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Oh, no! The twins are\Nnowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.67,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}W-What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:09.60,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}What in the world happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:14.61,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Long time no see, Doctor. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.61,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Have you already forgotten\Nabout those twins...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.29,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:30.02,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Save me, Doctor... I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.12,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.54,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I was supposed to have died that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:54.48,Monster - Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}You brought me back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:45.53,Monster - Time and Place,Time/Place,0,0,0,,{\pos(365,320)\fad(600,0)\fs45}Five Months Later
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like another scorcher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's summer,\Nyet you're all bundled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NThat paper's three days old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They say this time a middle-aged couple\Nin Verden was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the Killer is a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... You said you're going\Nto Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't know if\NI can meet up with him or not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go there...
